    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[1].entries.Array.size
      value: 3
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[2].entries.Array.size
      value: 2
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[3].entries.Array.size
      value: 2
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[4].entries.Array.size
      value: 9
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[5].entries.Array.size
      value: 9
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[6].entries.Array.size
      value: 2
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[7].entries.Array.size
      value: 10
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[8].entries.Array.size
      value: 5
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[9].entries.Array.size
      value: 4
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[10].entries.Array.size
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[11].entries.Array.size
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[0].entries.Array.data[0].text
      value: The story you will hear today, happened a long time ago.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[0].entries.Array.data[1].text
      value: The story of two women, who loved each other more than life.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[0].entries.Array.data[2].text
      value: What nonsense you utter, she is happy here. Happier than she ever was
        amongst your kind.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[0].entries.Array.data[3].text
      value: Lies! No one could be happy with a monster like you!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[0].entries.Array.data[4].text
      value: I, Sonnet, the greatest mage in the land, will make sure this fair maiden
        is rescued from your claws.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[0].entries.Array.data[5].text
      value: A beautiful girl like her deserves to be much more than just a blood
        supply for a monster.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[0].entries.Array.data[6].text
      value: What?! You would dare-! Bella, stay back, let me rid us of this pest.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[0].entries.Array.data[7].text
      value: Isa... be careful...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[0].entries.Array.data[8].text
      value: Worry not, my love, I promise, I will hurry back into your arms.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[1].entries.Array.data[0].text
      value: "The first of them, Isobel\u2014powerful, ruthless, living in her cold,
        lonely castle away from others. "
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[1].entries.Array.data[1].text
      value: Despite her wealth and the legion of servants there was no one that
        could bring her the warmth of human touch, she craved so immensely.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[1].entries.Array.data[2].text
      value: That was until Bella came into her life.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[2].entries.Array.data[0].text
      value: Bella was kind, warm and gentle, bringing Isobel everything the castle
        was missing.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[2].entries.Array.data[1].text
      value: It didn't take long for Bella's warmth to melt Isobel's long-frozen
        heart.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[2].entries.Array.data[2].text
      value: That was until Bella came into her life.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[3].entries.Array.data[0].text
      value: They lived happily for a long time, away from people and in peace.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[3].entries.Array.data[1].text
      value: They didn't yet know that their peace would soon be disturbed by an
        unwelcome guest.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[3].entries.Array.data[2].text
      value: It didn't take long for Bella's warmth to melt Isobel's long-frozen
        heart.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[4].entries.Array.data[0].text
      value: Foul beast! Come out and face me, so that I can end your wretched existence!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[4].entries.Array.data[1].text
      value: I have found your lair at last, and came here to free this poor, innocent
        girl!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[4].entries.Array.data[2].text
      value: What nonsense you utter, she is happy here. Happier than she ever was
        amongst your kind.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[4].entries.Array.data[3].text
      value: Lies! No one could be happy with a monster like you!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[4].entries.Array.data[4].text
      value: I, Sonnet, the greatest mage in the land, will make sure this fair maiden
        is rescued from your claws.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[4].entries.Array.data[5].text
      value: A beautiful girl like her deserves to be much more than just a blood
        supply for a monster.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[4].entries.Array.data[6].text
      value: What?! You would dare-! Bella, stay back, let me rid us of this pest.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[4].entries.Array.data[7].text
      value: Isa... be careful...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[4].entries.Array.data[8].text
      value: Worry not, my love, I promise, I will hurry back into your arms.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[5].entries.Array.data[0].text
      value: But hurry back she did not. The mage's attack brought her down, and
        before she knew, her body was broken, her soul starting to slip away.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[5].entries.Array.data[1].text
      value: ISOBEL!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[5].entries.Array.data[2].text
      value: Be calm, dear maiden, the foul beast is no more.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[5].entries.Array.data[3].text
      value: No...! No... please, no...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[5].entries.Array.data[4].text
      value: What? You would weep after that monster?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[5].entries.Array.data[5].text
      value: You must be enthralled, nothing else could explain this.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[5].entries.Array.data[6].text
      value: I must lock you here, for your own safety, until the creature's spell
        wears off.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[5].entries.Array.data[7].text
      value: "That very same \u201Ccreature\u201D was struggling to hold on, the
        last sparks of her undead life being extinguished."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[5].entries.Array.data[8].text
      value: The last thing she saw before dying was her beloved, being dragged away
        from her corpse, crying out for her.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[5].entries.Array.data[9].text
      value: The last thing she saw before dying was her beloved, being dragged away
        from her corpse, crying out for her.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[6].entries.Array.data[0].text
      value: The next thing she saw was red walls and flowing magma, as she woke
        up in Hell.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[6].entries.Array.data[1].text
      value: Even though her body fell, her soul persevered, holding on, dragging
        her to the fiery pits.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[6].entries.Array.data[2].text
      value: Be calm, dear maiden, the foul beast is no more.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[6].entries.Array.data[3].text
      value: No...! No... please, no...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[6].entries.Array.data[4].text
      value: What? You would weep after that monster?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[6].entries.Array.data[5].text
      value: You must be enthralled, nothing else could explain this.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[6].entries.Array.data[6].text
      value: I must lock you here, for your own safety, until the creature's spell
        wears off.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[7].entries.Array.data[0].text
      value: "I can\u2019t believe she\u2019s gone... my Isa..."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[7].entries.Array.data[1].text
      value: Quit your sobbing, my dear. Soon the spell will fade, and you will see
        that your so-called lover was nothing but a bloodsucking monster.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[7].entries.Array.data[2].text
      value: The only monster here is you.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[7].entries.Array.data[3].text
      value: "We\u2019ll work on that attitude."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[7].entries.Array.data[4].text
      value: You'll do no such thing, scum.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[7].entries.Array.data[5].text
      value: Isa...!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[7].entries.Array.data[6].text
      value: What?! How?! I killed you!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[7].entries.Array.data[7].text
      value: Clearly not well enough.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[7].entries.Array.data[8].text
      value: "Ugh! Doesn\u2019t matter. I\u2019ll do it again."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[7].entries.Array.data[9].text
      value: "And this time you\u2019re not coming back."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[8].entries.Array.data[0].text
      value: Isa!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[8].entries.Array.data[1].text
      value: You...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[8].entries.Array.data[2].text
      value: I...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[8].entries.Array.data[3].text
      value: I was sure I lost you.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[8].entries.Array.data[4].text
      value: I promised you I would be back, didn't I?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[8].entries.Array.data[5].text
      value: Isa...!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[8].entries.Array.data[6].text
      value: What?! How?! I killed you!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[8].entries.Array.data[7].text
      value: Clearly not well enough.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[8].entries.Array.data[8].text
      value: "Ugh! Doesn\u2019t matter. I\u2019ll do it again."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[8].entries.Array.data[9].text
      value: "And this time you\u2019re not coming back."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[9].entries.Array.data[0].text
      value: Never scare me like that again.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[9].entries.Array.data[1].text
      value: I will do my best.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[9].entries.Array.data[2].text
      value: And that is how this story ends.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[9].entries.Array.data[3].text
      value: The Lovers reunited.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[9].entries.Array.data[4].text
      value: The Magician defeated.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1840014530239347126, guid: a553583edd8f4ae46b8883c3c6c0c1c2, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLibrary.Array.data[10].entries.Array.data[0].text
      value: The Magician defeated.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
